### Demo 1: Sử dụng IEventPublisher trực tiếp
### services.AddScoped<IEventPublisher, OutboxEventPublisher>();
POST http://localhost:5003/api/policydemo/create-policy-simple
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "policyNumber": "POL-SIMPLE-001",
  "premium": 1000000,
  "productId": "PROD-LIFE-001",
  "customerId": "CUST-001"
}

### Demo 2: Sử dụng ITransactionalEventService (Khuyến nghị)
### Đảm bảo tính nhất quán giữa dữ liệu và events
POST http://localhost:5003/api/policydemo/create-policy-transactional
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "policyNumber": "POL-TRANS-001",
  "premium": 1500000,
  "productId": "PROD-HEALTH-001",
  "customerId": "CUST-002"
}

### Demo 3: Publish multiple events
POST http://localhost:5003/api/policydemo/create-policy-with-activation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "policyNumber": "POL-MULTI-001",
  "premium": 2000000,
  "productId": "PROD-AUTO-001",
  "customerId": "CUST-003"
}

### Check Outbox Status
GET http://localhost:5003/api/policydemo/outbox-status

### Test Multiple Policies
POST http://localhost:5003/api/policydemo/create-policy-simple
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "policyNumber": "POL-SIMPLE-002",
  "premium": 750000,
  "productId": "PROD-TRAVEL-001",
  "customerId": "CUST-004"
}

### Check Outbox Status Again
GET http://localhost:5003/api/policydemo/outbox-status

### Test Transactional with Different Data
POST http://localhost:5003/api/policydemo/create-policy-transactional
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "policyNumber": "POL-TRANS-002",
  "premium": 3000000,
  "productId": "PROD-INVESTMENT-001",
  "customerId": "CUST-005"
}

### Final Outbox Check
GET http://localhost:5003/api/policydemo/outbox-status